title: 2 Weeks Fishing, Hunting Crabbing in Florida. Florida Family Adventure
description:
We spent two weeks over Christmas and New Years exploring Florida. Fishing for sharks, sheepshead, mangrove snapper, catfish and more. Hunting alligators, crabbing and swimming with manatees. We have a an amazing Florida adventure. 

We have made several stand-alone videos from this trips on this channel and on my other YouTube channel (Catfish and Carp) - here are the links to those videos:
